column5: Heading up to Caribou Falls sept 21 - going thru Ft. Francis, Nestor Falls and Sioux Narrows. Any specific bait shops that sell leeches?
We have had good luck with "Anglers Pro Shop" on hwy 71 north of the falls in Nester Falls. 807-484-2525"Keep your bait in the water and your Butt in the Boat"Sprinter
